00:26:17.806 --> 00:26:19.556 A:middle
In order to fire a slingshot in

00:26:19.556 --> 00:26:21.246 A:middle
Swiftshot, the way you do it is

00:26:21.246 --> 00:26:22.586 A:middle
you move close to that

00:26:22.586 --> 00:26:23.136 A:middle
slingshot.

00:26:23.546 --> 00:26:24.266 A:middle
You don't have to pick which

00:26:24.266 --> 00:26:25.296 A:middle
slingshot you're going to fire

00:26:25.296 --> 00:26:25.976 A:middle
